data.description: Great starter home in Dunning!!! 2beds up + den in lower level, 2 full baths.  Lovely open floor plan upstairs with large living room and separate dining room with newer laminate flooring.  Two good size bedrooms and full bath.  Lower level is finished with large family room, additional bedroom and full bath.  Good storage throughout.  Large backyard.  2 car garage.  Property being conveyed As-Is.
